    "body": "@francoischalifour I don't think it's [an issue](https://preactjs.com/guide/differences-to-react#what-s-different-), it might be an expected behaviour. Indeed it's very specific to Preact like the issue we have. IMO it worth cover it with a test to avoid any regression in the future. We can reproduce the exact same logic that we have inside the Panel and test that the component is not re-created.",
